would just be different
modules within applications.

00:09:21.770 --> 00:09:27.410
And for him, the way he taught
it was very much through--

00:09:27.410 --> 00:09:29.209
kind of a socratic
method actually.

00:09:29.209 --> 00:09:30.750
You know, what
happens if we do this?

00:09:30.750 --> 00:09:31.979
What if we add this here?

00:09:31.979 --> 00:09:33.770
