different transformation?

00:09:33.770 --> 00:09:35.930
Why is it-- why is this working?

00:09:35.930 --> 00:09:38.770
Why are these mechanisms
attracting this way?

00:09:38.770 --> 00:09:40.760
I thought it actually
forced you to understand

00:09:40.760 --> 00:09:43.700
the intuition of the
principles behind what

00:09:43.700 --> 00:09:46.400
was going on the chalkboard,
which is why I think actually

00:09:46.400 --> 00:09:47.966
that tool is useful.

00:09:47.966 --> 00:09:49.340
But I think for
